whereas.text:
Whereas within the 2,000-year-old Sacred See of the
			 Ecumenical Patriarchate, the New Testament was codified and the Nicene Creed
			 was created;

Whereas Ecumenical Patriarch Bartholomew is one of the
			 world’s preeminent spiritual leaders and peacemakers representing over 300
			 million Orthodox Christians worldwide;

Whereas the Ecumenical Patriarchate has a record of
			 reaching out and working for peace and reconciliation amongst all faiths and
			 has fostered dialogue among Christians, Jews, and Muslims;

